        <mxCell id="hDbT7Zey_Wr_ot4flL9r-41" value="&lt;h3 style=&quot;&quot;&gt;This database stores players and their race attempts for the game built in &lt;span style=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot;&gt;Unity&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;The &lt;code data-end=&quot;222&quot; data-start=&quot;215&quot;&gt;Users&lt;/code&gt; table stores player information (email, name, tutorial status).&lt;br&gt;The &lt;code data-end=&quot;306&quot; data-start=&quot;292&quot;&gt;RaceAttempts&lt;/code&gt; table stores every race result (lap time and date).&lt;br&gt;There is a &lt;span data-end=&quot;405&quot; data-start=&quot;371&quot;&gt;one-to-many (1:N) relationship&lt;/span&gt; between Users and RaceAttempts:&lt;br&gt;One user can have many race attempts&lt;br&gt;Each race attempt belongs to exactly one user&lt;br&gt;The leaderboard is calculated dynamically by selecting the best (minimum) lap time for each user.&lt;/h3&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="175" width="510" height="250" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
